{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_03_03",
  "title": "鈴村優 3話 突然のお誘い",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスライブ、無事に終わって良かった……\n俺も仕事を終わらせて早く帰ろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m glad the Christmas concert went off so well.\nI’m going to finish up my work and head home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_keytap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 0.8
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6500.000000000001,
          "startTime": 11.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "鈴村さん達は、今頃楽しんでるかな\n――ん？　メッセージ？　鈴村さんからか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hope Suzumura and the others are having fun by now.\nHuh? A message? From Suzumura…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "――パーティー楽しんでますよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“We’re having fun at our party.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6466.666666599998,
          "startTime": 25.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "良かった。……えっと、返信は……\nおっと、電話か……もしもし？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s good. I should reply…\nHuh? A phone call… Hello.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1799.9999999999973,
          "startTime": 28.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、{user}さん、画像見ました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}‚ did you see the picture?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、ありがとう\n今、ちょうど返信しようと思ってたところだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ thank you.\nI was just about to write back to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、{user}さんは\n今どこにいてはるん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ {user}‚\nwhere are you now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "事務所だよ。もう帰るけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At the office‚ about to head home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "……事務所で何してはるん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What are you doing at the office?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "事務所ですることなんて、仕事に決まってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m at the office‚ so I’m working.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくのクリスマスやのに……\n寂しないん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it’s Christmas…\nAren’t you lonely?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "平気だよ。俺はこの仕事が好きだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m fine. I really love my job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、去年までのうちらもそうやったけど……\nあっ、いいこと思いついたわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I guess we were the same way up to last year…\nHey‚ I just thought of a good idea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、今からうちらのとこに来るのはどうやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about you come over to our place now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんやったら\n瑠依ちゃんもすみれちゃんも大歓迎や",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you come over‚ {user}‚\nRui and Sumire will be happy to see you too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "冗談はやめてくれ。こんな夜更けに\n若い女の子の部屋に行けるはずがないだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re kidding. No way I’m going to a young woman’s\nroom this late at night.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 83.2
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 83.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "なんでなん？　行けない理由でも……はっ！\nもしかして、うちに対してやましい思いがあるん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? Why? There’s no reason… Ah!\nDo you maybe have unspeakable feelings about me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 93.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "こんな時間にうちのとこに来たら我慢出来なくなるん？\nうちのこと、そんな風に思ってたんや……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You wouldn’t be able to hold it in if you came over to my place this late?\nSo that’s how you feel about me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことじゃない！\n世間的にダメなんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not like that!\nIt’s just socially unacceptable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 106.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、まぁせやね\n……ごめんなさい、冗談やん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ you’re right.\nSorry‚ I was just kidding.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 112.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "今夜は姉妹三人で楽しんでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You should have fun tonight with just you three girls.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "うん、{user}さん、今日のこと\nほんまにありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep! Hey {user}‚\nthanks for today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 120.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんから\n最高のクリスマスプレゼントをいただいたわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got the best\nChristmas present from you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 125.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "おおげさだな。君達の予定を元通りに戻しただけだよ\n夜更かしはし過ぎないように。また事務所で。おやすみ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re exaggerating. All I did was put your schedule back how it was.\nDon’t stay up too late. I’ll see you at the office. Goodnight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 136.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "はい、おやすみなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ good night.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "せやから、聞いてや～\n昨日、すみれちゃんが泣き出してな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now listen…\nSumire started crying yesterday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "何度も聞いたって。感激して泣いたんだろ\n嬉し泣きならいいじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve been saying that. She was moved to tears‚ right?\nIt’s good to cry with happiness.",
        "id": ""
      },
